---
title: Pepper Crusted Swordfish Steak with Mediterranean Salad
description: Firm and hearty, swordfish fries beautifully, making it the perfect centrepiece to this extravagant Mediterranean-inspired salad. While the flavours in this dish are exquisite, the meal takes only 30 minutes from pan to plate. To create this dish, simply roast red pepper and tomatoes to release their tender juiciness and ciabatta for a lovely crunchy texture. Drizzle in a tangy dressing and sprinkle feta, olives and walnuts to finish. Close your eyes on the first bite, and you can almost hear the gentle lapping of waves on the Mediterranean shore.
